{"tid":843710,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"外傭未經我批准就自己返左家鄉，可唔可以炒左佢而唔洗賠錢！？","createTime":"2018-10-01T10:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T21:39:19.000Z","uid":54025,"like":4,"dislike":149,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbfaa9155063e839bdd6c40c3d0a66dbc9b526d","tid":843710,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"如題，一早同佢講左依幾日3連休大陸有親戚落黎要佢幫低幫手，之後會補返假比佢。始終要請客多個人幫手爭好遠。<br />\n<br />\n但前日佢無啦啦走黎同我講家鄉出左事要即走，佢話地震海嘯個仔失左蹤。但個問題係佢一早應承左我會留低做野，我個時仲1516緊未批准佢走。但佢襯夜晚個時走左。之後whatsapp佢又唔回我。<br />\n<br />\n我真係好失望，點解依家d人咁無責任心，真係無可能原諒佢，依家炒就炒硬。想問下可唔可以因為佢擅離職守而唔洗賠一個月糧炒佢?"},{"pid":"5929e164b12c26cc0228e39438219890929696dc","tid":843710,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870d0c1055378d9b391ef53fcce70a3805b924e2","tid":843710,"uid":52087,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"你扮咩吖 有撚錢請賓賓咩你"},{"pid":"6db49009f581878bf0f1889cbdc56694cd7ca3ba","tid":843710,"uid":124941,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:56:33.000Z","msg":"假膠"},{"pid":"13f6bc038866a9c7f3fcb455d331c5196306d7cc","tid":843710,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"870d0c1055378d9b391ef53fcce70a3805b924e2","tid":843710,"uid":52087,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"你扮咩吖 有撚錢請賓賓咩你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:57:56.000Z","msg":"發覺請貴左，依家出緊5200比佢<br />\n<br />\n我炒左搵個件可以省返800一個月"},{"pid":"01319a19760773f343f19f5781fbafec12d34e4f","tid":843710,"uid":170044,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你輸波都唔洗係到扮有錢請賓妹黎玩呀"},{"pid":"957ca8238d883a96b7a5fc8cefb094dad9cd2432","tid":843710,"uid":170044,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"13f6bc038866a9c7f3fcb455d331c5196306d7cc","tid":843710,"uid":54025,"like":0